panels.description: Includes calls on hard phones and pre-5.5 softphones that were SIP based

targets.query: SELECT sum(activeCalls)*10000/$__interval_ms FROM "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and tenant <> '' and "hostname" =~ /^$server$/  GROUP BY tenant, time($__interval)

panels.title: Active SIP Calls on agents grouped by tenant

targets.query: SELECT sum(activeCalls)*10000/$__interval_ms   FROM "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ and "hostname" =~ /^$server$/  GROUP BY trunk, time($__interval)

panels.title: Active calls on trunks grouped by trunk

targets.query: SELECT difference(sum(totalCompletedCallAttempts))/6  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ group by trunk, time(1m)

panels.title: Successful call completions per minute - by trunk

panels.description: Include calls on 5.5+ softphones as well as nailed connections

targets.query: SELECT sum(activeVirtualCalls)*10000/$__interval_ms FROM "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and tenant <> '' and "hostname" =~ /^$server$/  GROUP BY tenant, time($__interval)

panels.title: Active Virtual (WebRTC) Calls on agents grouped by tenant

targets.query: SELECT difference(sum(totalCompletedCallAttempts))/6 + difference(sum(totalAbandonedCallAttempts))/6  + difference(sum(totalRejectedInviteResp))/6 from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ group by trunk, time(1m)

panels.title: Total call attempts per minute - by trunk

targets.query: SELECT difference(max(totalCompletedCallAttempts))*10000/$__interval_ms  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and tenant <> '' group by tenant, time($__interval)
SELECT difference(max(totalAbandonedCallAttempts))*10000/$__interval_ms  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ group by trunk, time($__interval)
SELECT difference(max(totalAbandonedCallAttempts))*10000/$__interval_ms  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and tenant <> '' group by tenant, time($__interval)
select difference(sum(totalRejectedInviteReq))/6  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ GROUP BY trunk, time(1m)
SELECT sum(activeCalls)*10000/$__interval_ms   FROM "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and trunk <> '' and "hostname" =~ /^$server$/  GROUP BY hostname, time($__interval)

targets.query: select difference(sum(totalRejectedInviteResp))/6  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ GROUP BY errorCode, time(1m)
SELECT difference(sum(totalRegisters))*10000/$__interval_ms  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and tenant <> '' group by hostname, time($__interval)
select difference(sum(totalRejectedInviteResp))/6  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter AND errorCode = '503'  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ GROUP BY trunk, time(1m)
SELECT difference(sum(totalRegisters))*10000/$__interval_ms  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter and tenant <> '' group by tenant, time($__interval)
select difference(sum(totalRejectedInviteResp))/6  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter AND errorCode = '403'  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ GROUP BY trunk, time(1m)
select difference(sum(totalRejectedInviteResp))/6  from "sipprocessor.trunk" WHERE $timeFilter AND errorCode = '480'  and "trunk" =~ /^$trunk$/ GROUP BY trunk, time(1m)
